before the deadline. 2. If step 1 is completed, she must dispel

one of Sadi's requests, she can be told one digit \c

ハヤトとメリルのルール

1. Merill will monitor Hayato. 2. Hayato will wait in the cage
until Seria decrypts the code. 3. Hayato may support Seria from
inside the cage \c[27] if \c he wants. 4. Direct attacks on each
other are prohibited. In that case, Seria will be executed.
5.\c[27] Direct contact with \cHayato from Merill is prohibited.

Seria \c[27]If these rules are followed, \cHayato should still be
